who managed the slush fund.

97
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,300
Kang Se Ri is also the murderer...

98
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,440
who killed my son, Eun Ho.

99
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,580
On the USB drive
containing this video,

100
