of all cash and valuables I gave them.

103
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,390
Finally,

104
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:00,390
to Ms. Kim Do Hee...

105
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,090
and to her family,

106
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,000
I offer my sincerest apologies.

107
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:19,310
What's happening?

108
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,650
That crazy jerk.

109
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,550
On the cell phone
Kang Se Ri regularly used,

110
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:32,390
there's the original dashcam footage
from Ms. Kim Do Hee's accident.

111
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:35,130
