to Ms. Kim's family.

113
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:43,470
She also told loan shark Hong Man Su
to commit and cover up her crimes.

114
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:49,040
We confirmed the number was used
to pose as a cop and call Ms. Kang.

115
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:52,040
Upon hearing of Kang Se Ri's arrest,

116
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:54,250
Hong Man Su also confessed
to all his crimes.

117
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,180
