125
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:19,540
No!

126
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:24,940
Kang Jae In.

127
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,980
Kang Jae In, this is all your fault!

128
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:29,350
This is all because of you!

129
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:32,220
Kang Jae In,
you should've been the one to die!

130
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:33,950
Why should I have to die?

131
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:36,190
- This is all your fault!
- Order in the court!

132
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:40,120
- You! It's all your fault!
- Order!

133
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,730
Remove the defendant.
I order her removed from the court.

134
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:44,530
Hey!

135
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:48,300
