138
00:08:58,780 --> 00:09:01,180
That witch, Kang Se Ri,
tried to change the beneficiary.

139
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:03,710
I'm so glad I changed it right back.

140
00:09:07,450 --> 00:09:09,120
He's gone now,

141
00:09:09,990 --> 00:09:11,320
