261
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:25,310
I take this role with a great sense
of responsibility.

262
00:18:26,110 --> 00:18:28,480
I'll honor our late chairman's legacy,
Kang Gyu Cheol.

263
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:32,020
By providing the highest quality
and exceptional service,

264
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:35,250
we will expand beyond Korea
and onto the world stage.

265
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:38,720
I will do my best to lead YL Group
toward that future.

266
00:18:40,590 --> 00:18:41,730
Thank you.

267
00:18:52,870 --> 00:18:54,870
You've heard of
Doctors Without Borders, right?

268
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:57,570
Yes. Why do you ask all of a sudden?

269
00:19:01,810 --> 00:19:03,150
That's right.

270
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:07,020
I've decided to volunteer abroad.
I leave tomorrow.

271
00:19:08,450 --> 00:19:09,990
So soon?

272
00:19:10,690 --> 00:19:12,160
Does your family know?

273
00:19:12,390 --> 00:19:15,660
I've told my uncle,
and I'll to tell my mom today.

274
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:19,200
I dropped a few hints,
but I doubt she caught on.

275
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:24,170
Why the sudden decision?

276
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:26,400
Is it because of me?

277
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:31,110
So much has happened this year,
it's been overwhelming.

278
00:19:32,340 --> 00:19:33,880
I just need to clear my head.

279
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:39,820
Of course, my feelings for you
are a factor too.

280
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:43,390
I'm not saying I'm giving up on you.

281
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:46,490
I just want to take some time
to do some soul-searching.

282
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:51,300
Along the way, I lost my composure
and got too hasty.

283
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:55,070
If you came to be with me
only because I pressured you,

284
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:58,170
we'd both just end up miserable,
wouldn't we?

285
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,570
I'll be gone for about a year.

286
00:20:04,340 --> 00:20:07,180
I need to find some peace
and get my thoughts in order.

287
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:11,650
I'll be ready for your answer then.

288
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:14,690
You take your time and think too.

289
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:27,130
Wait.
This is where the princess lives.

290
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:29,500
Gi Man. Listen.

291
00:20:30,630 --> 00:20:32,170
Stay right here, okay?

292
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,940
I'll go get you
your favorite ice cream.

293
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:36,640
Okay.

294
00:20:37,570 --> 00:20:39,340
He's not a normal kid,

295
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:41,910
so they won't let him starve,
will they?

296
00:20:43,410 --> 00:20:45,620
Goodbye, Gi Man.

297
00:20:46,180 --> 00:20:48,520
Go live with that princess
you love so much.

298
00:20:49,290 --> 00:20:51,460
Look. I'm leaving now.

299
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,020
You just stay right here.

300
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,970
Oh, it's you, Princess!

301
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:11,170
I didn't come here
to see you, Princess.

302
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:13,780
I won't cause you any trouble.

303
00:21:24,990 --> 00:21:27,320
We'll take good care of him.
Don't you worry.

304
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:37,630
How could she just abandon
her own son?

305
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:43,210
This was in Gi Man's bag.
A note asking me to care for him.

306
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:49,450
It's a good thing I had someone
tailing her, just in case.

307
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:51,450
Sister...

308
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:53,950
Force of habit.

309
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:56,420
So, Hwang Na Ra
went to study abroad?

310
00:21:57,050 --> 00:21:58,490
She said
she wanted to study fashion.

311
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:00,420
An opening came up,
so she had to go.

312
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:01,890
I told her to.

313
00:22:03,690 --> 00:22:06,800
Is Gi Man staying
at the community center?

314
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:10,700
Yes. There's a doctor on-site,

315
00:22:10,770 --> 00:22:14,340
He can get rehab, so he'll be okay.
Don't worry too much.

316
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:17,170
Okay.

317
00:22:17,910 --> 00:22:21,080
Getting him away from Noh Sook Ja
is a relief in itself.

318
00:22:22,380 --> 00:22:25,050
I hope Noh Sook Ja
gets what's coming to her.

319
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:34,490
I'm not tied down anymore.

320
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:39,030
I'm Noh Sook Ja.
With this deposit money,

321
00:22:39,130 --> 00:22:42,030
turning it into 10 or 20 times the amount
is a piece of cake.

322
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:47,370
Thief! Stop him! My money!

323
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:52,140
Darn it!

324
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:55,080
My money!

325
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,450
My money.

326
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:06,060
Medical volunteer work,
all of a sudden?

327
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:07,960
And you're leaving tomorrow?

328
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:10,260
I'm sorry I didn't tell you sooner.

329
00:23:10,730 --> 00:23:12,460
I was afraid you'd be against it.

330
00:23:13,930 --> 00:23:15,400
But still...

331
00:23:15,870 --> 00:23:18,400
What's the big rush?

332
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:20,800
It all happened so fast.

333
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:23,510
The doctor there got sick and left,

334
00:23:23,510 --> 00:23:25,180
and they couldn't leave
the position open.

335
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:29,780
You've long wanted to volunteer,
and done it occasionally,

336
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:32,050
so I had a feeling
this might happen.

337
00:23:33,380 --> 00:23:34,850
But is this because of Jae In?

338
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:37,250
No.

339
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,620
You just said it yourself, Mom.

340
00:23:40,060 --> 00:23:44,090
I've thought of this since college,
and this seems like a good chance.

341
00:23:47,430 --> 00:23:48,900
It's not a dangerous place, is it?

342
00:23:49,670 --> 00:23:50,830
No, it's not.

343
00:23:51,230 --> 00:23:53,540
Even though it's volunteer work,
I'm mostly going to get some rest.

344
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,440
All right.

345
00:23:56,940 --> 00:23:58,280
If you're so set on it,

346
00:23:59,710 --> 00:24:00,840
then I guess you have to go.

347
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:58,440
(Chairman Kang Jae In)

348
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,810
Dad.

349
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:09,080
I've finally taken back YL Group.

350
00:25:10,350 --> 00:25:12,150
From this position that you built,

351
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,350
I'll prove to everyone...

352
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:16,490
that YL Group is still going strong.

353
00:25:29,870 --> 00:25:34,370
(1 year later)

354
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:38,640
Do it right!

355
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:42,580
Level 3, not 1.
Fill the whole space, top to bottom.

356
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:54,790
Lunchtime!

357
00:25:56,460 --> 00:25:57,690
Chair.

358
00:26:14,010 --> 00:26:16,410
You've got to eat
to keep your strength up.

359
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:20,720
Thank you.

360
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,890
Eat up!

361
00:26:44,540 --> 00:26:45,640
Ta-da!

362
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:48,880
I won an award
at the Draw Your Dream Contest.

363
00:26:50,050 --> 00:26:52,150
"Designer Kim Bo Ram, Designer?"
Gosh.

364
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:54,380
So your dream is to be a designer,
Bo Ram.

365
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,890
Yes. Just like Ms. Jae In,

366
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:58,760
I'm going to be a great designer.

367
00:27:00,690 --> 00:27:03,260
Grandma Ja Young,
did I do a good job?

368
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:06,330
You did a wonderful job.

369
00:27:06,930 --> 00:27:09,270
You could be a designer already.

370
00:27:10,670 --> 00:27:13,470
- Want to see my other drawings?
- Sure.

371
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:20,610
Your mother seems to be doing
much better.

372
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:24,650
Yes, it's all thanks to Bo Ram.
She visits so often.

373
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:28,150
Having her as company
while she writes and draws...

374
00:27:28,150 --> 00:27:29,450
seems to be helping.

375
00:27:29,650 --> 00:27:31,250
That's such a relief.

376
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:34,890
Ja Young.
We're moving into a new house soon,

377
00:27:34,890 --> 00:27:37,760
so you, Seung Woo, and Jae In
have to come to our housewarming.

378
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:39,060
Okay?

379
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,630
Of course.

380
00:27:41,430 --> 00:27:43,830
Then I guess we'll need
to buy a housewarming gift for you.

381
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:46,770
You coming is the best gift.

382
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,140
Really?

383
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:12,060
Yes, Jae In. I'm on my way now.

384
00:28:13,630 --> 00:28:15,500
That's right. Just wait there.

385
00:28:16,300 --> 00:28:17,530
I'll be there soon.

386
00:28:20,370 --> 00:28:22,110
Just wait a little longer, Jae In.

387
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:24,410
I've got a big surprise for you.

388
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:29,850
How about going
for a round of golf sometime?

389
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:33,320
I've never played.
I wonder if I'd be any good.

390
00:28:34,050 --> 00:28:35,390
I can teach you.

391
00:28:36,020 --> 00:28:38,460
Then maybe I'll take you up on that.

392
00:28:41,930 --> 00:28:43,490
Your temp for the day is here!

393
00:28:44,330 --> 00:28:47,600
Hey. Thanks to you,
I can play golf today.

394
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,070
Thanks.

395
00:28:49,130 --> 00:28:52,040
Don't mention it.
Call me anytime I have a day off.

396
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,700
Okay, I appreciate it.

397
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,870
- I'll get going.
- Okay, have fun.

398
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,350
So, what should I start with?

399
00:29:07,020 --> 00:29:08,120
Seung Woo!

400
00:29:08,490 --> 00:29:11,420
Na Ra, I thought you were studying
in the States.

401
00:29:11,490 --> 00:29:13,560
I'm on break and came back for a bit
to see my brother.

402
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:16,160
My brother was craving the chicken
from here.

403
00:29:17,190 --> 00:29:19,160
Half fried, half seasoned.

404
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:21,500
A Coke for me,
and a Coke Zero for my ugly sister.

405
00:29:23,570 --> 00:29:25,200
I'll have that right out for you.

406
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:27,570
You guys go ahead and catch up.

407
00:29:28,910 --> 00:29:30,310
Have a seat over here.

408
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:37,010
So, how is studying in the States?

409
00:29:37,310 --> 00:29:38,720
It must be tough,
everything being so new.

410
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,420
The first few months
were a bit tough,

411
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:41,750
but I'm fine now.

412
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:44,250
You're still at the same company, right,
Seung Woo?

413
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:48,220
We have more new employees now,
and I'm their mentor.

414
00:29:48,490 --> 00:29:51,160
I chew them out until they're bawling,

415
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:53,430
then I buy them coffee to make up.

416
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:55,000
I guess I'm a real adult now.

417
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:15,320
I'll bring back lots of yummy snacks
for you.

418
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:17,090
- Chocolate.
- Oh, sure.

419
00:30:17,090 --> 00:30:19,620
- The last one was so good.
- Got it.

420
00:30:20,890 --> 00:30:22,190
What's wrong? Aren't you coming?

421
00:30:24,090 --> 00:30:25,230
Poor thing.

422
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,540
Here, get yourself something to eat.

423
00:30:37,170 --> 00:30:38,170
Let's go.

424
00:30:47,950 --> 00:30:48,950
Oh, dear.

425
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:00,260
("YL's Kang Jae In
Named Businessperson of the Year")

426
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:03,200
Those were the best of my gory days.

427
00:31:04,330 --> 00:31:07,240
It's glory days, not gory days.

428
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:08,910
Don't use words you don't know.

429
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,870
Darn it. Shut your mouth.

430
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:12,880
How many times do I have to say it?

431
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:16,180
I'm telling you, that Kang Jae In
was my daughter-in-law.

432
00:31:17,210 --> 00:31:21,750
My late son was supposed to be
the chairman of YL Group,

433
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:25,390
but that wicked Kang Jae In
tricked him and stole it all!

434
00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:28,420
Really? My son is the chairman
of Samdong Group.

435
00:31:28,930 --> 00:31:31,160
And you know my daughter
is the chairwoman of Sinnara Group, right?

436
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:34,330
You're all full of nonsense.

437
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,930
All of you, shut your mouth.

438
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,000
It's been a while.

439
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:41,660
Have you been well?

440
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,270
You're back?

441
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:50,470
Yes.

442
00:32:57,610 --> 00:32:58,950
Jae In, can I...

443
00:33:01,850 --> 00:33:03,020
try to win your heart from now?

444
00:33:09,260 --> 00:33:10,330
I missed you...

445
00:33:12,730 --> 00:33:13,730
so much.

446
00:35:02,370 --> 00:35:05,070
(We'd like to thank all our viewers
for supporting Queen's House.)

447
